</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-iapVNj iUcVvL pf-110_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Maximise_Flexibility_in_Health_and_Social_Care_Training_with_Blended_Learning_-_Dr_Richard_Dune.jpg?v=1724314600" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Maximise_Flexibility_in_Health_and_Social_Care_Training_with_Blended_Learning_-_Dr_Richard_Dune.jpg?v=1724314600 1536w" width="1105" height="740" alt="Maximise flexibility in health and social care training with blended learning - Dr Richard Dune -" title="Maximise flexibility in health and social care training with blended learning - Dr Richard Dune -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-bVHBsO cFdcpI pf-111_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-gFVuLS jpmtwg pf-112_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by YuriArcursPeopleimages via Envato Elements</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-114_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-iapVNj iUcVvL pf-115_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/The_Importance_of_Relevance_in_Health_and_Social_Care_Training_for_Adults_-_Dr_Richard_Dune.jpg?v=1724314600" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/The_Importance_of_Relevance_in_Health_and_Social_Care_Training_for_Adults_-_Dr_Richard_Dune.jpg?v=1724314600 1536w" width="1981" height="1321" alt="The importance of relevance in health and social care training for adults - Dr Richard Dune -" title="The importance of relevance in health and social care training for adults - Dr Richard Dune -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-bVHBsO cFdcpI pf-116_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-gFVuLS jpmtwg pf-117_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by Pressmaster via Envato Elements</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data