</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-iapVNj iUcVvL pf-130_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Blended_Learning_Approaches_for_Health_and_Social_Care_Professionals_-_Dr_Richard_Dune.jpg?v=1724314601" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Blended_Learning_Approaches_for_Health_and_Social_Care_Professionals_-_Dr_Richard_Dune.jpg?v=1724314601 1536w" width="1711" height="1142" alt="Blended learning approaches for health and social care professionals - Dr Richard Dune -" title="Blended learning approaches for health and social care professionals - Dr Richard Dune -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-bVHBsO cFdcpI pf-131_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-gFVuLS jpmtwg pf-132_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by AydinovKamran via Envato Elements</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-134_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-iapVNj iUcVvL pf-135_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/How_to_Design_Effective_Health_and_Social_Care_Training_for_Adult_Learners_-_Dr_Richard_Dune.jpg?v=1724314600" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/How_to_Design_Effective_Health_and_Social_Care_Training_for_Adult_Learners_-_Dr_Richard_Dune.jpg?v=1724314600 1536w" width="1766" height="1179" alt="How to Design effective health and social care training for adult learners - Dr Richard Dune -" title="How to Design effective health and social care training for adult learners - Dr Richard Dune -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-bVHBsO cFdcpI pf-136_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-gFVuLS jpmtwg pf-137_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by LightFieldStudios via Envato Elements</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-iapVNj iUcVvL pf-139_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kAkozD kgiAhT pf-140_ pf-heading-1-h3">The path forward
